CATCAS_SERIES_PARALLEL_RELATION 1
TYPE BOOLEAN_F3
NODE A EXTERNAL
NODE B EXTERNAL
NODE U INTERNAL
NODE W INTERNAL
NODE Z INTERNAL
RELATION R_AU A U 0 1 2 0
RELATION R_UW U W 0 1 2 0
RELATION R_WB W B 0 1 2 0
RELATION R_UZ U Z 0 1 2 0
RELATION R_ZB Z B 0 1 2 0
ELIMINATE U
ELIMINATE W
ELIMINATE Z
END
